title: Trump says U.S. will decertify Canadian-made planes, threatens 50% tariff
summary_full: The president accused Canada of blocking the sale of U.S.-made Gulfstream aircraft and said he would raise tariffs in the latest dispute to rock the once-chummy relationship.
